        {
            "id": 6007736,
            "title": "〈焦點股〉jpp-KY 5月營收創新高無畏關稅戰 股價飆逾8%",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>jpp-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5284:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5284\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5284-TW</a>)(經寶精密) 公布 5 月合併營收衝上 2.88 億元，月增 12.98%，年增 94.21%，再創新高紀錄，激勵今 (5) 日盤中股價大漲超過 8%，創 3 月下旬來新高價；經寶表示，在 AI 伺服器和航太二大主軸產品的驅動下，全年接單將持續暢旺，新廠房正緊鑼密鼓建置中。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007736%2Fl%2F715a152198cffeeecce88715d5054334.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007736%2Fl%2F715a152198cffeeecce88715d5054334.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007736%2Fl%2F715a152198cffeeecce88715d5054334.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007736%2Fl%2F715a152198cffeeecce88715d5054334.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007736%2Fl%2F715a152198cffeeecce88715d5054334.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007736%2Fl%2F715a152198cffeeecce88715d5054334.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007736%2Fl%2F715a152198cffeeecce88715d5054334.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007736%2Fl%2F715a152198cffeeecce88715d5054334.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007736%2Fl%2F715a152198cffeeecce88715d5054334.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007736%2Fl%2F715a152198cffeeecce88715d5054334.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007736%2Fl%2F715a152198cffeeecce88715d5054334.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007736%2Fl%2F715a152198cffeeecce88715d5054334.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007736%2Fl%2F715a152198cffeeecce88715d5054334.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007736%2Fl%2F715a152198cffeeecce88715d5054334.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007736%2Fl%2F715a152198cffeeecce88715d5054334.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007736%2Fl%2F715a152198cffeeecce88715d5054334.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007736%2Fl%2F715a152198cffeeecce88715d5054334.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">經寶5月營收創新高紀錄。(鉅亨網資料照)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>經寶累計前 5 月合併營收 13.54 億元，年增 48.32%。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>經寶說明，隨著客戶積極布建 AI 伺服器與資料中心，帶動通用型 AI 伺服器機櫃與通用型機殼、CDU 與冷熱分歧管等精密機構件等強勁需求，AI 伺服器訂單持續湧入，產能擴充也同步進行中。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>經寶第一季已啟動第二座自動化噴烤漆廠建設，預計最快明年初可投入量產，將有效緩解現有產線瓶頸。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>航太業務方面，經寶除穩定供應 Airbus、Thales 體系客戶，與新客戶 Safran 合作持續進展，並積極推進歐盟航太 POA(維修與改裝) 認證申請，預計未來可切入高附加價值的維修與改裝市場。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>經寶將於 6 月 16 日參加 2025 年法國巴黎航太展，藉此展現多元產品能量與技術實力，並爭取國際合作機會。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>對於匯率變動影響，經寶也說明，本位貨幣為<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/thbusd\">泰銖</a>，營收和成本皆以<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/thbusd\">泰銖</a>計價，且航太業務雖以美元結算，但在美元資產和美元負債相抵後淨額占比不大，整體匯率變動對實質營運影響有限。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6007736",
            "pub_date": "2025-06-05 09:49:01",
            "source": "cnyes",
            "kind": 1,
